blog.name: httpwritings
blog.title: Requests Are Open!!
blog.description: Hey guys!! I’ll try to post as much as I can, so I apologize for any delays!! I write for many fandoms, so check out my post about it. Also, requests are always open unless stated otherwise!

tags: king arthur the legend of the sword
body:
Hello guys!!

So I guess you could say I’m kinda new (not really) to the writing community here!! I actually ran a blog called @imaginessforall or something like that a few years back, and I finally decided to get back into writing again!! I hope that you guys will like the blog!!

Oh, I also have a small list of fandoms that I’ll start off writing for, so please send in any requests that you may have, I’m opened to anything!!

  • Marvel (mostly venom and avengers right now ://)
  • Some DC (just ask!!)
  • King Arthur (Charlie Hunnam one lmaooo)
  • Lord of the Rings/The Hobbit
  • Harry Potter

So yeah, I’ll be updating some more stuff for the blog tomorrow. Until then, send in any requests that you guys have!! I hope you enjoy the blog!!

summary: "Fondue" continues to be an in-joke amongst the Avengers.
body:
“Fondue” continues to be an in-joke amongst the Avengers.

At some point, Tony had heard the story from his father, and asked Steve if it was true.

Everyone was thoroughly amused, and it continues to be used as a codeword.
